              <p>Get all software & loaders for <b>StarSat</b> receivers in one place.</p>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
                <a href="/software?brand=StarSat" class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4">Get Software</a>
                <a href="/loader?brand=StarSat" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4">Get Loader</a>
